OOC: I always use automatic guns.  Sorry if it seems extreme to you, but its 
just how i battle.

:::Maximus Prime/The Protectrons/Torca/Ratchet/Sideswipe/Sky 
Lynx/Orion/Atma/Psuedo:::

::My Maximals see that the battle is over.  Maximus Prime separates.  Sky 
Lynx transforms into shuttle mode and Torca, Ratchet and Sideswipe climb in, 
and he takes off.  The others get into shuttles and they all head back to the 
CF::
~~~~~
Psuedo: Well, its good that you had friends to keep you company.
Atma: How have you caused them trouble?
